质。 反观肉食动物，像狼，狼头总是先吃内脏，吃饱后，才轮的着 「 狼腿子门 」，可见它们对内脏的偏爱。 明明很有营养，也有动物喜欢吃，为什么人类就讨厌。 那么，动物内脏本身的味道为什么让人类讨厌。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-59c6377bb7dfa6f818127a9dad6c04a6_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "474 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/450789032"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0dHWit3StcJ4EAMaCDYyNDU0Mzc0IO2R5YIGMBc4pwNADXIJNDUwNzg5MDMyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1616660016.5033462", "card_id": "Q_430872977", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 159}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么裸辞的几乎都很久找不到工作？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "身边有个朋友，28 岁，大概从今年五月份裸辞至今依旧没找到下一份工作，也变得越来越抑郁，觉得即将步入 30 岁的行列，却一事无成，不甘心从事一眼就能看到头的工作，大一点的公司自己又进不去。关于这件事你怎么看？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c7dc0a8317db1416d973e29529649635_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "403 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/430872977"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0dHWit3StcJ4EAMaCDU4MDI4ODg0IJ7S0/0FMAw4uAdADnIJNDMwODcyOTc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1616660016.5041418", "card_id": "Q_381497547", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 386}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果给蜀军提供不限量的肯德基和麦当劳，诸葛亮选择哪款快餐才能更快击败曹魏？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如题 蜀军更喜欢麦乐鸡还是香辣鸡翅呢"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-8483fe831eed1be6ae99141423217530_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "364 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/381497547"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI0dHWit3StcJ4EAMaCDQ3MDU1NjU3IMDU2/MFMEE4mQdAD3IJMzgxNDk3NTQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_16166